OL,3,CHygiene poverty keeping kids out of
OL,4,Cthe classroom, leading charity says
OL,6,FAn organisation working to tackle
OL,7,Fhygiene poverty has warned that
OL,8,Fincreasing numbers of young people in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland are going without
OL,10,Fbasic essentials like shower gel,
OL,11,Fdeodorant and toothpaste.
OL,13,FNew research from The Hygiene Bank
OL,14,Festimates that a third of
OL,15,Fschoolchildren are experiencing
OL,16,Fhygiene poverty.
OL,18,FThose tackling the issue on the ground
OL,19,Fsay it is leading to social exclusion,
OL,20,Fincreased absences and reduced
OL,21,Foutcomes for pupils.
