OL,3,CHygiene poverty keeping kids out of
OL,4,Cthe classroom, leading charity says
OL,6,FA study from The Hygiene Bank has
OL,7,Ffound that:
OL,9,F"It might mean young people having to
OL,10,Fgo to their first day at school
OL,11,Fwithout brushing their teeth or not
OL,12,Fbeing able to have a shower the night
OL,13,Fbefore and that has quite a profound
OL,14,Fimpact", Ruth Brock, CEO of The
OL,15,FHygiene Bank explained.
OL,17,FEileen Brown manages Dungannon Hygiene
OL,18,FBank. She has seen first hand the
OL,19,Fimpact that hygiene poverty can have
OL,20,Fon struggling families.
