OL,4,Cthe classroom, leading charity says
OL,6,FDrumglass High School has been working
OL,7,Fin partnership with The Hygiene Bank
OL,8,Ffor a number of years.
OL,10,FVice Principal Aisling Irvine told UTV
OL,11,Fthat hygiene poverty can lead to
OL,12,Flearning time being lost.
OL,14,F"There is a social issue, there is a
OL,15,Fbullying aspect that can become
OL,16,Fassociated with that and then it leads
OL,17,Fon to an attendance issue. People not
OL,18,Fcoming to school.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
