OL,3,CHygiene poverty keeping kids out of
OL,4,Cthe classroom, leading charity says
OL,6,F"If we have young people not accessing
OL,7,Flearning, if they are not in the
OL,8,Fbuilding, that means when it comes to
OL,9,Fassessments their attainment and
OL,10,Facademic outcomes are reduced.
OL,12,F"If we can offer free products to
OL,13,Fthose in need that is absolutely
OL,14,Ffantastic, but as a whole school
OL,15,Fcommunity we find that these products
OL,16,Fhave given us an opportunity to
OL,17,Feducate", she said.
OL,19,FSt Patrick's Academy is receiving
OL,20,Fdonations this year for the first time.
